Introduction:

With the advancements in information technology and web applications, the way information / data is shared have changed . With the changes in technology, web applications are becoming more prevalaent in businesses. 
Demands form users also changed, individuals want to access their data anywhere and anytime. With the changes in the digital world, businesses are also changing their ways, online banking systems, 
and onlineshopping websites have emerged which makes it more convenient for some people who would want to do certain things in the comfort of their own homes.  Though these advancements provide convenience and efficieny for end users, these advancements
 attracted people who intend to do malicious activities like Hackers, Cyber criminals, 
and Scammers which led to the birth of Web Application and Security.
